name: The Road #3
description:
The Road #3 is an ongoing mini series based on the escapades of the past and future. 

Every image shot out the window while driving somewhere.

Waiting for a train to pass deeeep in the Mojave Desert.

Iris Demant - hotter than Mojave in my heart, blaring from the speakers and on repeat the entire time we drove through this desert (played 169 times). Great song and great desert ::: )

Shot on - Nikon AF with Ektar 100 film
